  Upon his arrival to Tehran, Mr. Bolkiah said that the 
expansion of relations in all fields was the most important aim 
of his visit to our country. 
  Mr. Hashemi-Rafsanjani spoke on the visit of the sultan of 
Brunei, saying: 
  [Begin Rafsanjani recording] Brunei is an Islamic country, 
