<H3> <TI>   Further Cooperation Welcomed </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0302234094 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
First Program Network in Persian 2030 GMT 3 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0302234094 </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
