   Elliott Abrams
   Pleads Guilty
   In Contra Case
   ---
   State Department Aide Hid
   Data on Efforts to Arm
   Anti-Sandinista Fighters
   ----
   By David Rogers
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
10/08/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A4
</SO>
<MS>
